text: Ellicott's Mills Historic District is a historic district in Oella, Maryland, United States. It is on the east bank of the Patapsco River, opposite Ellicott City. This historic district is on the National Register of Historic Places. ==References== ==Other websites== *, including photo from 1982, at Maryland Historical Trust *Boundary Map of the Ellicott's Mills Historic District, Baltimore County, at Maryland Historical Trust Category:Historic districts in the United States Category:National Register of Historic Places Category:1775 establishments in the Thirteen Colonies Category:1770s establishments in Maryland
